event_name: New Years Eve Swing Dance & Concert feat. Lloyd Arntzen, Kelby MacNayr w dance lesson
location: 511 Michigan ST, VICTORIA, BC, V8V1S1, CA
description: A Swinging Celebration of the year that was and a chance to swing in the new year with live music from 9-12 and a dance lesson from 8-9 pm led by Joel and Louise Schwarz. Featuring performances by Lloyd Arntzen, Kelby MacNayr, and more. Indoor shoes are required for dancing. All ages, bodies, and abilities welcome.
